63 Forest Ave., north side, between Duer Lane and Haven Esplanade, showing the Louis A. Dreyfus residence.

May 1927.

P. L. Sperr.

(1) Forest Ave. (background), west from Duer Lane to Haven Esplanade. The houses are on the north side of the avenue. The view is across the northeastern edge of Silver Lake Park.
